Players traditionally name their decks. With the On the Edge e-mail discussion list, the Edge folder on America On-line, and other media, League members can brag about their decks and conquests. At conventions, players can meet like gunslingers to duke it
\hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0 out. 
